nay-Llinares FJ (2025) Addendum: Evidence for transmission of <italic toggle="yes">Taenia solium</italic> taeniasis/cysticercosis in a rural area of Northern Rwanda. <italic toggle="yes">Front. Vet. Sci</italic>. 12:1579712. doi: <ext-link xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="https://doi.org/10.3389/fvets.2025.1579712" ext-link-type="uri">10.3389/fvets.2025.1579712</ext-link>.</p></body></article></pmc-articleset>